RTCDataChannelNegotiated.summary:
The read-only RTCDataChannel property
negotiated indicates whether the
's connection was negotiated by the Web app
(true) or by the WebRTC layer (false). The
default is false.

remarks.para: See Creating a data channel for further information about this property.

RTCDataChannelNegotiated.value:
true if the 's connection was negotiated by
the Web app itself; false if the negotiation was handled by the WebRTC
layer. The default is false.
